videos.description: Nigel Hayes shows off his explosiveness by racing right past the defender and throwing down the dunk with the foul for Wisconsin.
videos.headline: Hayes blows past defender for the dunk and the foul

videos.description: Micah Potter blocks Ethan Happ, allowing Marc Loving to convert a fastbreak layup on the other end
videos.headline: Marc Loving gets the layup on the break

videos.description: Bronson Koenig saves the ball from going out of bounds and turns it into an amazing assist
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig gets a ridiculous assist on Jordan Hill 3-pointer

videos.description: OHIO STATE blocks consecutive shots with great team defense
videos.headline: OHIO STATE blocks consecutive shots with great team defense

videos.description: Bronson Koenig is unphased by defender in his face and he buries a fadeaway 3-pointer
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig is unphased by defender in his face and he buries a fadeaway 3-pointer

videos.description: Nigel Hayes gets out on the break as he gets the bucket and draws the foul
videos.headline: Nigel Hayes absorbs contact and gets the bucket

videos.description: Bronson Koenig buries a three off a beautiful crossover dribble to push WISCONSIN's lead to 18
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig channels his inner Steph Curry, buries a stepback 3-pointer off the dribble

videos.description: Bronson Koenig caps off his 15-point first half with another big 3-pointer
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig is feeling it as he buries another three just before the half

videos.description: Bronson Koenig continues his lights out shooting from beyond the arc, 21 points on the night.
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig is in the zone, drains another 3

videos.description: Bronson Koenig builds on 15-point first half perfromance with another 3
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig is ON FIRE, buries another contested 3-pointer

videos.description: Ohio State tries to deny Nigel Hayes getting inside, but one quick hesitation move has Hayes past the defender and throwing down another big dunk of Wisconsin.
videos.headline: No stopping Hayes on the way to two-handed slam

videos.description: With Wisconsin running the fast break, Zak Showalter throws up the underhand lob to the flying Khalil Iverson for the massive alley-oop finish.
videos.headline: Iverson throws down vicious alley-oop dunk in Wisconsin win

videos.description: Bronson Koenig finds Brevin Pritzl with a gorgeous bounce pass for the lay-in
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig finds Brevin Pritzl with a gorgeous bounce pass for the lay-in

videos.description: Bronson Koenig breaks down his 21-point performance that powered Wisconsin past Ohio State 89-66
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig breaks down his 21-point game against OSU
